@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-8">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="bg-primary-600 px-8 py-20 text-white border-b border-primary-700">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-3">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
            <p class="text-primary-100 font-medium text-lg">Sukkur IBA University HelpDesk & Complaint Management</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="p-8 space-y-8 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            
            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">1. Information Collection</h2>
                <p>We collect information primarily to process, track, and resolve your complaints effectively. This includes your student or staff email address (e.g., domain <code>@@siba.edu.pk</code>), user credentials, and the specifics of any complaints or tickets you file within the system.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">2. Use of Information</h2>
                <p>The information submitted is utilized exclusively for internal university administration purposes. Administrators review ticket details to allocate resources, address your specific concerns, and improve overall campus services. We do not use this data for external marketing.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">3. Data Security and Access</h2>
                <p>Your data is secured using standard encryption practices. Access to your complaints is strictly limited to authorized SIBA administrative staff. Senior administrators have oversight to ensure all inquiries are handled securely and fairly.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">4. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You reserve the right to review the status of your complaints simply by logging into your dashboard. If you believe any account info is incorrect or needs removal (e.g., upon graduation or departure from the university), you may contact the Senior Admin directly.</p>
            </section>

            <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl border border-primary-100 text-primary-800 text-center font-medium">
                If you have any questions regarding how your data is handled, please reach out to <a href="mailto:senior@admin.siba.edu.pk" class="font-bold underline hover:text-primary-900">senior@admin.siba.edu.pk</a>.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
